*{{cite book|title=The Branches of Heaven: A History of the Sung Imperial Clan|year=1999|publisher=[[Harvard University Press]]|isbn=}}
::Chinese translation: {{cite book|title=''天潢貴胄：宋代宗室史''|isbn=9787214040978|translator=Zhao Dongmei|publisher=Jiangsu People's Publishing House|year=2006}}.

He also edited one volume of ''[[The Cambridge History of China]]'' (with [[Denis Twitchett]]).

